# hx boost


+htmx


/Users/michal/zettel/20251225122423-htmx-template-fragments-go


https://htmx.org/attributes/hx-boost/

The key here is that normal anchor and form tags are boosted to use AJAX instead.
HTMX requests are not affected, so if they're the only one used, then there is no
point in using it. This works nicely as a fallback if the user has no Javascript
enabled. If js is enabled, then AJAX will be used for normal anchor and form tags.
